    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《风水喵将》是一款独特的<u><i>轻肉鸽棋牌游戏</i></u>，融合了传统麻将机制、Roguelike式的养成进程与神秘的风水策略。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个策略性的回合制系统中，你将重新诠释古老的麻将玩法 —— 利用固定的14张手牌进行排列组合，构建<i>吃（Chi）</i>、<i>碰（Pong）</i>与<i>对子（Pair）</i>等组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时，激活强大的风水宝物效果，管理技能卡，挑战不断升级的敌人。每一局都考验你的布局智慧、应变能力与策略思维。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/ef1b41034502a138ba634c82a6a14959.avif?t=1770886324\" width=600 height=108 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无需麻将经验</strong>，简单上手，深入难精。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将东方传统与现代Roguelike完美结合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随进度推进，挑战难度逐步上升，策略不断演化！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/8ded10cad9f4bb0c1b01b9c61dddbfe1.avif?t=1770886324\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/b9ed43489386910d87076952ebaf2644.avif?t=1770886324\" width=600 height=108 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战胜敌人可解锁全新宝物、卡牌与效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过各种宝物提升分数与番，<strong>实现大数字跳跃</strong>！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/be422e3d5b8dfcd026db77c12ba131f3.poster.avif?t=1770886324\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/be422e3d5b8dfcd026db77c12ba131f3.webm?t=1770886324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/be422e3d5b8dfcd026db77c12ba131f3.mp4?t=1770886324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/450a4ca538b308e6cc4b60436d6ad63c.avif?t=1770886324\" width=600 height=108 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集并使用技能卡操控牌面、提升得分、改变宝物效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宝物之间可产生强力联动效果，组合出不同流派与打法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高重复游玩价值，<strong>每局都有新组合、新构筑与新挑战</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/ad5de72a8b919ac9722329821b895b13.poster.avif?t=1770886324\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/ad5de72a8b919ac9722329821b895b13.webm?t=1770886324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/ad5de72a8b919ac9722329821b895b13.mp4?t=1770886324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/aebec8f6ff4433de97cabdb376cb5a98.avif?t=1770886324\" width=600 height=108 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拖动排列，组合成顺子、碰、对子。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险皆不同：随机的牌面、敌人、宝物与卡牌选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>摒弃牌河只有四张的固有思想</strong>，体验推牌出14张东风的快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/2df32508a2ae295ad471bc6b7e13000b.poster.avif?t=1770886324\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/2df32508a2ae295ad471bc6b7e13000b.webm?t=1770886324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/2df32508a2ae295ad471bc6b7e13000b.mp4?t=1770886324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/42f28950681bfa2e9f9e392abbce6f6e.avif?t=1770886324\" width=600 height=108 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将神秘宝物放置在八方位，时刻注意宜与忌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典猫meme和像素结合，<strong>TA居然是这个技能——</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >风水宝物间形成连携，打造专属打法流派！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/61b6b9bca5eb8d6ceddf6c1b9efe2839.poster.avif?t=1770886324\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/61b6b9bca5eb8d6ceddf6c1b9efe2839.webm?t=1770886324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332060/extras/61b6b9bca5eb8d6ceddf6c1b9efe2839.mp4?t=1770886324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >风里雨里，我们在喵将先锋群里等你！😽<u><strong>QQ群号：723156944</strong></u></p>",
